            . I am a <rs id="t18300708-49-viclabel279" type="occupation">journeyman carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-49-victim387 t18300708-49-viclabel279"></join>. On the 31st of May I lost the tools mentioned, which I had left on the Saturday evening in the attic at the <placeName id="t18300708-49-crimeloc280">Marquis of Tavistock's house</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300708-49-crimeloc280" type="placeName" value="Marquis of Tavistock's house"></interp>
