                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-49-off277 t18300708-49-crimeloc280"></join> - the house was not finished; these are the tools - I saw them at Bow-street; these brad-awls have my name on them, and I know the other- I lost the same number of things which were found; I know nothing of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300708-49-person391">
                  GEORGE 
                  VICK
               <interp inst="t18300708-49-person391" type="surname" value="VICK"></interp>
